而无需经历通常的延迟。&lt;footer&gt;&lt;cite&gt;Sandra Notardonato&lt;br/&gt;全球合作伙伴发展与影响者关系负责人, 高知特&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/footer&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;svg height="16" viewbox="0 0 37 31" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;&lt;path d="M16.7999 4.81642C14.2986 5.45109 12.1333 6.45909 10.3039 7.84042C8.51192 9.18442 7.13059 10.8644 6.15992 12.8804C5.18926 14.8964 4.70392 17.1738 4.70392 19.7124H3.47192C3.47192 18.1444 3.95726 16.8938 4.92792 15.9604C5.93592 14.9898 7.27992 14.5044 8.95992 14.5044C10.3786 14.5044 11.6853 14.8591 12.8799 15.5684C14.0746 16.2778 15.0266 17.2298 15.7359 18.4244C16.4453 19.6191 16.7999 20.9258 16.7999 22.3444C16.7999 23.7631 16.4453 25.0698 15.7359 26.2644C15.0266 27.4591 14.0746 28.4111 12.8799 29.1204C11.6853 29.8298 10.3786 30.1844 8.95992 30.1844C7.24259 30.1844 5.69326 29.7364 4.31192 28.8404C2.96792 27.9444 1.90392 26.6938 1.11992 25.0884C0.373255 23.4831 -7.79331e-05 21.6911 -7.79331e-05 19.7124C-7.79331e-05 16.3524 0.690589 13.3097 2.07192 10.5844C3.49059 7.82175 5.45059 5.54442 7.95192 3.75242C10.4906 1.92309 13.4399 0.672418 16.7999 0.000417709V4.81642ZM36.9599 4.81642C34.4586 5.45109 32.2933 6.45909 30.4639 7.84042C28.6719 9.18442 27.2906 10.8644 26.3199 12.8804C25.3493 14.8964 24.8639 17.1738 24.8639 19.7124H23.6319C23.6319 18.1444 24.1173 16.8938 25.0879 15.9604C26.0959 14.9898 27.4399 14.5044 29.1199 14.5044C30.5386 14.5044 31.8453 14.8591 33.0399 15.5684C34.2346 16.2778 35.1866 17.2298 35.8959 18.4244C36.6053 19.6191 36.9599 20.9258 36.9599 22.3444C36.9599 23.7631 36.6053 25.0698 35.8959 26.2644C35.1866 27.4591 34.2346 28.4111 33.0399 29.1204C31.8453 29.8298 30.5386 30.1844 29.1199 30.1844C27.4026 30.1844 25.8533 29.7364 24.4719 28.8404C23.1279 27.9444 22.0639 26.6938 21.2799 25.0884C20.5333 23.4831 20.1599 21.6911 20.1599 19.7124C20.1599 16.3524 20.8506 13.3097 22.2319 10.5844C23.6506 7.82175 25.6106 5.54442 28.1119 3.75242C30.6506 1.92309 33.5999 0.672418 36.9599 0.000417709V4.81642Z" fill="currentColor"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;我们正在帮助客户自信地扩展 AI——建立在稳健的治理、安全性和设计信任的基础上。我们专门的 Anthropic 卓越中心加速了准备和能力建设，与印孚瑟斯 AI 优先的价值理念保持一致。通过团队在实际交付中应用 Claude Code，我们正在帮助客户在各个行业释放 AI 价值。&lt;footer&gt;&lt;cite&gt;Anand Swaminathan&lt;br/&gt;执行副总裁兼全球通信、媒体与技术负责人, 印孚瑟斯&lt;/cite&gt;&lt;/footer&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/article&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>